<i>noun</i>: 환락 [활락], 유희 [유히], 위락 [위락], 오락성 [오ː락썽] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>환락 [활락]</dt><br>
<dd>pleasure; amusement; delight</dd><br>
<dd>매우 기뻐하고 즐거워함. 또는 매우 기쁘고 즐거운 것.</dd><br>
<dd>A state of being extremely happy and delightful; or a source of such a happiness and delight.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>유희 [유히]</dt><br>
<dd>game; amusement</dd><br>
<dd>장난을 치며 즐겁게 놂. 또는 그런 놀이.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of having fun while romping, joking, etc., or such playful activity.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>위락 [위락]</dt><br>
<dd>recreation; amusement</dd><br>
<dd>시설 등을 이용하여 편안하게 쉬면서 피로를 풀고 즐김.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of having a good time while relaxing, relieving fatigue by using a facility, etc.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>오락성 [오ː락썽]</dt><br>
<dd>entertainment; amusement</dd><br>
<dd>즐기며 기분을 즐겁게 할 수 있는 성질.</dd><br>
<dd>The quality of being amusing and diverting.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>